'''Stickers''' is a social feature, that allows users to place images on surfaces within [[Worlds|worlds]]. Stickers come with one default set at a time. Occasionally, limited-time sticker sets release, replacing the default set. One sticker can be placed per user at a time. Stickers can also overlap other users' stickers.

== Default stickers ==
The default set of stickers is themed around the VRChat mascots, [[VRCat]] & [[VRRat]]. There are 9 stickers in this set, and is currently the default set.
