== Custom stickers ==
Users with VRC+ can create and place custom stickers using the [[Inventory|inventory]], [[Camera|camera]], or by uploading images after logging in on the VRChat website. There is a limit of 18 custom stickers that can be uploaded at a time.

== Sticker effects==
Sticker effects are effects that are visible on the sticker, these are applied to Exclusive, or Shop stickers to distinguish itself from Custom Stickers. Effects can be filtered on the inventory page.

Known effects include "Holographic" and "Lenticular".

*Holographic: applies a sheen, with a unique texture overlaying the sticker. 
*Lenticular: allows the sticker to be seen differently depending on the angle it's viewed from.

